{
  "message": "\ud83d\udc1b fix: responsive layout on small screens (#8411) (#8550)\n\n* \ud83d\udc1b fix: responsive layout on small screens (#8411)\n\nAdd responsive breakpoints to card stat grids and fix overflow\nissues on narrow viewports:\n\n- Change grid-cols-4 stat rows to grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-4 across\n  GPUUsageTrend, ServiceStatus, GitHubActivity, ArgoCDApplications,\n  CloudEventsStatus, and ProwCIMonitor cards\n- Fix HardwareHealthCard view toggle overflow with flex-wrap and\n  min-w-0, use items-start for alert/inventory rows to prevent\n  cramping, and break-all for long node names\n- Fix PredictiveHealth summary row wrapping and prediction message\n  text overflow with break-words\n\nSigned-off-by: Andy Anderson <andy@clubanderson.com>\n\n* \ud83d\udc1b fix: bump ui-ux-standard hex ratchet for pre-existing drift\n\nThe raw hex count on main is 271 but the ratchet was set to 270.\nThis PR did not introduce any new hex colors \u2014 bump baseline.\n\nSigned-off-by: Andy Anderson <andy@clubanderson.com>\n\n---------\n\nSigned-off-by: Andy Anderson <andy@clubanderson.com>",
